item.title: About me
item.description: I am Sabarno Saha, a student at IISER-Kolkata studying anything and everything I like. I like Physics and Maths. When I am not studying, which is often, I like quizzing, watching TV Shows and watching random game dev videos on YouTube. I like coding sometimes. My computer runs Arch Linux with Hyprland. I use nvim as my text editor, mostly for writing LaTex stuff.
